'''Denice Klarskov''' (born 18 April 1986) is a Danish [[pornographic actress]] and [[entrepreneur]].
==Life and career== Klarskov started her career at 16 as a photo [[Model (profession)|model]], appearing in several major magazines and entering the finals of the beauty contest [[:da:Miss Solskin|Miss Solskin]].<ref name=dndn>Tine Bendixen (February 8, 2010), "[http://www.b.dk/personlig-udvikling/jeg-naar-aldrig-at-taenke-paa-det-som-sex »Jeg når aldrig at tænke på det som sex«]", ''[[Berlingske]]''. Retrieved 5 May 2013.</ref> She starred in her first [[pornographic film]] at the age of 18 years.<ref name=bbbio/> In 2004, she moved to [[Los Angeles]] where she worked for several years in the American adult industry.<ref name=bbbio>{{cite news|last=Kristian Villesen, Rasmus Bo Sørensen|title='Jeg er ret hårdfør'|url=http://www.information.dk/136326|accessdate=5 May 2013|newspaper=[[Dagbladet Information]]|date=February 16, 2007}}</ref>
Klarskov is the founder and the owner of "''DK Production''", a Danish porn production company.<ref>{{cite web|title=Jeg har trukket pornoen op på et andet niveau|url=http://ekstrabladet.dk/flash/dkkendte/article1361950.ece|publisher=''[[Ekstra Bladet]]''|accessdate=26 June 2011|authorlink=Morten Germund|language=Danish|date=2010-06-13}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Jesper Vestergaard Larsen|title=Får råd af Riskær|url=http://www.bt.dk/kendte/faar-raad-af-riskaer|publisher=''[[B.T. (tabloid)|B.T.]]''|accessdate=10 November 2011|language=Danish|date=3 December 2009}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=En dag på pornofabrikken|url=http://ekstrabladet.dk/flash/kultur/article1361981.ece||newspaper=''Ekstra Bladet''|accessdate=10 November 2011|last=Morten Germund}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Sushi-Denice har ændret vilkår i porno-branchen|url=http://www.mja.dk/artikel.php?node_id=17926&click_origin=article_related_article_1|publisher=''[[:da:Midtjyllands Avis|Midtjyllands Avis]]''|accessdate=10 November 2011|language=Danish}}</ref>
She has worked one week as a guest radio hostess for the radio show ''Anne og de herreløse hunde - nu uden Anne'' on [[HIT FM Denmark|ANR (Aalborg Nærradio)]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Pornoskuespiller er programleder |url=http://www.radioassistant.com/RA/2011/11/pornoskuespiller-er-programleder/ |publisher=''RadioAssistant'' |accessdate=10 November 2011 |author=Endre Juel Lundgren |date=7 November 2011 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120405025856/http://www.radioassistant.com/RA/2011/11/pornoskuespiller-er-programleder/ |archivedate=5 April 2012 |df= }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Nye værter på ANR |url=http://www.nordjyske.dk/artikel/10/5/28/3996924/3/nye%20v%E6rter%20p%E5%20anr |archive-url=https://archive.is/20120904180948/http://www.nordjyske.dk/artikel/10/5/28/3996924/3/nye%20v%E6rter%20p%E5%20anr |dead-url=yes |archive-date=4 September 2012 |publisher=''Nordjyske'' |accessdate=10 November 2011 |author=Ida Amalie Bodh Have |language=Danish |date=3 November 2011 |df= }}</ref> In 2012, Klarskov was the subject of an episode of [[:da:Emil Thorup|Emil Thorup]]'s documentary series ''Emils damer'', broadcast by [[DR HD]].<ref>{{cite news|last=Susanne Nielsen|title=Emil lægger an på porno-Denice|url=http://tvtid.tv2.dk/nytomtv/article.php/id-50031390:emil-l%C3%A6gger-an-p%C3%A5-pornodenice.html|accessdate=5 May 2013|newspaper=[[TV 2 (Denmark)|TV Tid]]|date=April 30, 2012}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Troels Trier|title=TV: Pornostjerne udfører dildoshow på DR|url=http://ekstrabladet.dk/flash/filmogtv/tv/article1750817.ece|accessdate=5 May 2013|newspaper=[[Ekstra Bladet]]|date=April 30, 2012}}</ref>
