'''Raffaele Cicala''' is an Italian [[business executive]] working in [[Europe]]. Since 2011, he has occupied the positions of CEO of the LaSer Group<ref name="Lesechos0203002630038">{{cite web|url=http://www.lesechos.fr/15/09/2013/lesechos.fr/0203002630038_raffaele-cicala-----comme-un-coup-dans-l-estomac--.htm|title=Raffaele Cicala : "?Comme un coup dans l?estomac?"|publisher=lesechos.fr|author=Les Echos|accessdate=29 April 2014}}</ref> and of LaSer Cofinoga.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.lasergroup.eu/fileadmin/administration/Fichier_Groupe/pdf/communiques_2011/Raffaele_Cicala.pdf |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2014-04-29 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110626153831/http://www.lasergroup.eu/fileadmin/administration/Fichier_Groupe/pdf/communiques_2011/Raffaele_Cicala.pdf |archivedate=2011-06-26 |df= }}</ref>
== Biography ==
After obtaining his degree, in 1985, he joined [[Procter & Gamble]] [[Italy]] and quickly reached the position of Group Manager.<ref name="24-7pressrelease">{{cite web|url=http://www.24-7pressrelease.com/press-release/worldwide-whos-who-names-raffaele-cicala-ceoexecutive-of-the-year-in-finance-320587.php|title=Worldwide Who's Who Names Raffaele Cicala, CEO,Executive of the Year in Finance|publisher=24-7pressrelease.com|accessdate=2014-04-29}}</ref> In 1989, he joined The [[Boston Consulting Group]] (BCG)<ref name="lsa-conso">{{cite web|url=http://www.lsa-conso.fr/raffaele-cicala-directeur-general-de-laser-un-specialiste-du-credit-face-a-de-nouveaux-defis,123062|title=Raffaele Cicala, directeur général de Laser...|publisher=lsa-conso.fr|accessdate=2014-04-29}}</ref> as a consultant assigned to the [[Paris]] office where his prime areas of focus were consumer goods and retail. In 1991, he returned to Italy with the opening of BCG office in Milan and contributed to its expansion by using his experience and knowledge to the benefit of industrial and financial entities. In 1997, he set The [[Boston Consulting Group]] office up in [[Warsaw]] of which he became Managing Partner, working throughout [[Eastern Europe]]. He worked as advisor to the [[Warsaw Stock Exchange]], on its development and privatization strategy.<ref name="wbj">{{cite web|url=http://www.wbj.pl/article-15745-ebrd-makes-a-move-on-warsaw-stock-exchange.html|title=Warsaw Business Journal - Online Portal - wbj.pl|publisher=wbj.pl|accessdate=2014-04-29|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140308022143/http://www.wbj.pl/article-15745-ebrd-makes-a-move-on-warsaw-stock-exchange.html|archivedate=2014-03-08|df=}}</ref> In 2001, he returned to [[Italy]] where he set the [[Rome]] office up. In 2006, Raffaele Cicala joined the [[Unicredit Group]], his former client<ref name="ilsole24ore">{{cite web|url=http://archivio-radiocor.ilsole24ore.com/ctgr-difesa-686/boston-consulting-group/|title=>> Difesa, Boston Consulting Group Notizie su Difesa, Boston Consulting Group pubblicate da Radiocor|publisher=archivio-radiocor.ilsole24ore.com|accessdate=2014-04-29}}</ref> he assisted for many years with its international growth strategy. While there, he occupied a number of positions before becoming Executive [[Vice-President]], and obtaining seat on the Group’s Executive Management Committee and on the Executive Committee for the [[retail banking]] branch as head of the [[Unicredit Group]] Household Financing Division.<ref name="businessweek">{{cite web|url=http://investing.businessweek.com/research/stocks/people/person.asp?personId=58204313&ticker=UCG:IM|title=Raffaele Cicala: Executive Profile & Biography - Businessweek|publisher=investing.businessweek.com|accessdate=2014-04-29}}</ref> In 2010, he published a report, “Rapporto sul Credito alle Famiglie” (“Report on Credit to Households”),<ref name="unicredit">{{cite web|url=https://uninews.unicredit.eu/it/articoli/primopiano/interventi/?ida=12965|title=Interventi : Italiani e credito: ecco cosa &egrave; cambiato - UniNews|publisher=uninews.unicredit.eu|accessdate=2014-04-29}}</ref> on the evolution of customer profiles in the consumer [[credit market]] in [[Italy]]. In 2011, he was appointed CEO of the LaSer Group,<ref name="e-marketing">{{cite web|url=http://www.e-marketing.fr/Article-A-La-Une/Raffaele-Cicala-le-nouveau-dg-de-LaSer-2537.htm|title=Raffaele Cicala, le nouveau dg de LaSer - e-marketing.fr|author=e-marketing 2014. All rights reserved. William Ramarques|publisher=e-marketing.fr|accessdate=2014-04-29}}</ref> a joint venture of [[Galeries Lafayette]] and [[BNP-Paribas]] Personal Finance,<ref name="lefigaro">{{cite web|url=http://www.lefigaro.fr/mon-figaro/2013/12/23/10001-20131223ARTFIG00253-laser-cofinoga-le-retour-en-forme-divise-les-actionnaires.php|title=LaSer Cofinoga : le retour en forme divise les actionnaires|publisher=lefigaro.fr|accessdate=2014-04-29}}</ref> a leading player in the consumer credit market and a provider of services to large retailers.<ref name="lopinion">{{cite web|url=http://www.lopinion.fr/3-fevrier-2014/raffaele-cicala-nous-ne-sentons-pas-tout-reprise-croissance-8849|title=Raffaele Cicala: " Nous ne sentons pas du tout la reprise de la croissance " &#124; L&#039;Opinion|publisher=lopinion.fr|accessdate=2014-04-29}}</ref> In December 2012, Raffaele Cicala, in collaboration with several enterprises, created the Manège de Chaillot Trust Fund, with the objective of providing support to create and stage productions for the [[Théâtre National de Chaillot]] in Paris (Chaillot National Theatre). He was elected Chairman of the Board of Directors of the Manège du Chaillot Trust Fund.<ref name="theatre-chaillot">{{cite web|url=http://theatre-chaillot.fr/laser|title=LaSer &#124; Théâtre National de Chaillot|publisher=theatre-chaillot.fr|accessdate=2014-04-29}}</ref>
== Functions and offices == *CEO, LaSer *CEO, LaSer Cofinoga *Member of Executive Committee, [[Galeries Lafayette]] group *Member of the Board, Solfea Bank *CEO, Sygma Banque *Chairman, LaSer Loyalty *Permanent representative of LaSer on the Supervisory Board of Xange Capital *Member of the board, LaSer Nederland BV *Member of the board, Ekspresbank *Member of the board, LaSer Nordic Services *Chairman of the Board of Directors, Manège de Chaillot
